Steps for building the source code
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

1. Install the required RPMs as shown below:

    $ sudo yum install epel-release
    $ sudo yum install python-Levenshtein
    $ sudo yum install -y libtool
    $ sudo yum install -y doxygen
    $ sudo yum install -y python-pep8
    $ sudo yum install -y openssl-devel
    $ sudo yum install -y graphviz
    $ sudo yum install -y check-devel

2. Change directory to the root of the SSPL source.

    $ /.../sspl
    $ ./jenkins/build.sh

3. RPMs will be genrated in dist/rpmbuild/RPMS/ folder.

    $ find dist/rpmbuild/RPMS -name "*.rpm"
    dist/rpmbuild/RPMS/noarch/sspl-ll-1.0.0-11.el7.noarch.rpm
    dist/rpmbuild/RPMS/x86_64/libsspl_sec-1.0.0-1.el7.x86_64.rpm
    dist/rpmbuild/RPMS/x86_64/libsspl_sec-debuginfo-1.0.0-1.el7.x86_64.rpm
    dist/rpmbuild/RPMS/x86_64/libsspl_sec-method_none-1.0.0-1.el7.x86_64.rpm
    dist/rpmbuild/RPMS/x86_64/libsspl_sec-method_pki-1.0.0-1.el7.x86_64.rpm
    dist/rpmbuild/RPMS/x86_64/libsspl_sec-devel-1.0.0-1.el7.x86_64.rpm
